// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2692 — Mass File Rename (dispossessor)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5eb39943-0049-5025-b222-03cedaa0ab46

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
